    "16438314992c9f9321": {
      "type": "accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "164383149952b74e7a-0": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does a pet grooming service take?",
            "description": "<p>The amount of time a grooming service takes depends on your pet's size and the type of service requested. Your stylist will be able to provide an estimated time of completion at check-in or over the phone.<br/><br/>Minor services, such as nail trimmings, approximately take 5 minutes and, depending on salon availability, no appointment is necessary. However, we recommend calling your local salon to confirm availability.</p>"
          }
        },
        "164383149952b74e7a-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I get my pet started with a grooming service?",
            "description": "<p>For dogs, we offer online booking on Minion. If you'd like to chat with a stylist about your pet's specific needs, call your local salon.</p>"
          }
        },
        "164383149952b74e7a-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I change or cancel an appointment?",
            "description": "<p>Please call your salon to cancel or make changes to your appointment.</p>"
          }
        },
        "3147fc3b-05fb-4a1f-93dd-0c157f542e91": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is safety ensured for all pet grooming services?",
            "description": "<p>We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of animal care and safety in the industry, as developed under the supervision of our Director of Veterinary Medicine, with counsel from several independent experts in animal care, behavior and ethics.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
